    h2 Assignment 3
    h4 Animation
    p.
      Animate your own character (Use a character you made in the exercises or make a new one)
    p.
      Your character should be able to do at least 3 things: walk, jump, and some movement that relates to the nature of
      your character (i.e. a crab might be able to pinch it's claws)
    p.
